{"name":"vi","desc":"vi 是一个功能强大的文本编辑器，可以在命令行中使用。它的功能包括文件编辑、搜索和替换、文本格式化等。","usages":[{"form":{"":{"name":"文件路径","required":true,"type":"string"},"-a":{"type":"check","name":"使用附加缓冲区","optionName":"-a"},"-A":{"type":"check","name":"使用大写字母 G","optionName":"-A"},"-b":{"type":"check","name":"在每行前面显示行号","optionName":"-b"},"-c":{"type":"check","name":"打印出文件中匹配的行数","optionName":"-c"},"-d":{"type":"string","name":"设置删除标记","optionName":"-d"},"-D":{"type":"check","name":"删除行","optionName":"-D"},"-e":{"type":"check","name":"等价于“-E”选项","optionName":"-e"},"-E":{"type":"check","name":"在每行末尾显示 $ 符号","optionName":"-E"},"-f":{"type":"string","name":"使用文件名列表查找字符串","optionName":"-f"},"-F":{"type":"check","name":"将字符串视为固定字符串而非正则表达式","optionName":"-F"},"-g":{"type":"check","name":"打印所有匹配的行","optionName":"-g"},"-h":{"type":"check","name":"不打印文件名","optionName":"-h"},"-H":{"type":"check","name":"强制打印文件名","optionName":"-H"},"-i":{"type":"check","name":"忽略大小写","optionName":"-i"},"-I":{"type":"check","name":"禁用智能缩进","optionName":"-I"},"-j":{"type":"check","name":"将多个文件的结果合并成一行","optionName":"-j"},"-k":{"type":"check","name":"配置交换文件","optionName":"-k"},"-l":{"type":"check","name":"仅打印包含匹配项的文件名","optionName":"-l"},"-L":{"type":"check","name":"仅打印不包含匹配项的文件名","optionName":"-L"},"-m":{"type":"string","name":"限制搜索的行数","optionName":"-m"},"-n":{"type":"check","name":"在每行前面显示行号","optionName":"-n"},"-N":{"type":"check","name":"禁用多重缓冲区编辑模式","optionName":"-N"},"-o":{"type":"check","name":"仅打印匹配项","optionName":"-o"},"-p":{"type":"string","name":"指定打印机类型","optionName":"-p"},"-P":{"type":"check","name":"使用 Perl 正则表达式语法","optionName":"-P"},"-q":{"type":"check","name":"仅打印错误消息","optionName":"-q"},"-r":{"type":"check","name":"递归搜索子目录","optionName":"-r"},"-s":{"type":"check","name":"禁用警告铃声","optionName":"-s"},"-S":{"type":"check","name":"禁用 shell 命令","optionName":"-S"},"-t":{"type":"string","name":"指定标签栏宽度","optionName":"-t"},"-T":{"type":"string","name":"指定终端类型","optionName":"-T"},"-u":{"type":"check","name":"禁用撤消功能","optionName":"-u"},"-U":{"type":"check","name":"启用撤消功能","optionName":"-U"},"-v":{"type":"check","name":"反向查找","optionName":"-v"},"-V":{"type":"check","name":"显示版本信息","optionName":"-V"},"-w":{"type":"check","name":"禁用换行符","optionName":"-w"},"-x":{"type":"check","name":"打印出完全匹配的行","optionName":"-x"},"-X":{"type":"check","name":"禁用剪贴板","optionName":"-X"},"-y":{"type":"check","name":"禁用对文件的写入","optionName":"-y"},"-Y":{"type":"check","name":"启用对文件的写入","optionName":"-Y"},"-z":{"type":"check","name":"打印出空行","optionName":"-z"},"-Z":{"type":"check","name":"禁用压缩文件","optionName":"-Z"}}}],"content":"<h2 id=\"例子\">例子</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>打开文件：<code>vi filename</code></li>\n<li>保存修改：在命令模式下输入 <code>:w</code> 或 <code>:wq</code></li>\n<li>不保存修改直接退出：在命令模式下输入 <code>:q!</code></li>\n<li>搜索文本：在命令模式下输入 <code>/text</code>，回车后会跳到第一个匹配的文本处，可以使用 <code>n</code> 和 <code>N</code> 来跳转到下一个或上一个匹配</li>\n<li>替换文本：在命令模式下输入 <code>:s/old/new/g</code>，其中 <code>old</code> 是要被替换的文本，<code>new</code> 是新的文本，<code>g</code> 表示全局替换</li>\n<li>复制粘贴：在命令模式下将光标移动到要复制的文本上，输入 <code>yy</code> 复制当前行，输入 <code>y</code>+<code>n</code>+<code>y</code> 复制 n 行，然后将光标移动到要粘贴的位置上，输入 <code>p</code> 粘贴</li>\n<li>撤销操作：在命令模式下输入 <code>u</code></li>\n<li>退出 vi：在命令模式下输入 <code>:q</code>，如果有修改过则会提示保存，否则直接退出</li>\n</ul>\n"}